item.title: Algorithm Series - DP
item.description: Question Definition(T & S) Given N, Find the total number of unique BSTs that can be made using values from 1 to N Examples: Input: n = 3 Output: 5 For n = 3, preorder traversal of 1. 1 2 3 2. 1 3 2 3. 2 1 3 4. 3 1 2 5. 3 2 1 Input: 4 Output: 14 Problem Analysis(A) At first, i did not quite understand what the question means.
